# assets/ directory (inside the skill)
#
# Put the templates the skill creates or reads at runtime: task logs, ADRs, PR
# bodies, etc. Common formats: .md, .json, .yaml, .txt. Reference them from SKILL.md
# with relative links.
#
# This folder lives inside skills/<skill-name>/ so those relative links keep working.
#
# Delete this file when you add your first real template, or remove the folder if the
# skill uses none.
